    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-01-05T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-01-05T16:00:00-05:00" n="300"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d300">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/1–552: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Acting Chairman of the United States Delegation to the
                        General Assembly</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1952-01-05T22:00:00+01:00"
                            >January 5, 1952—10 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 879. Re Ital membership in <gloss
                        target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>. Belaunde told Gross that he had met De Gasperi
                    and discussed tactics re Italy’s admission to <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss>.
                    Belaunde reported that De Gasperi had asked him not to press his plan but to let
                    things proceed for a while as they are. Belaunde seemed undetermined exactly how
                    to handle his item when it is reached. We will keep in close touch with him.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
